column5: Three friends travel to a small town where they meet Ragini, a beautiful woman. However, they soon realise that she has brought nothing but trouble in their lives.
Ramu yearns to play football while his brother, Deva, wants a bicycle. The brothers are happy when they find an abandoned bicycle, but things start to go wrong when it is stolen from them.
Entertainment-based programme.
Arav, an ambitious man, travels to the US to seek better opportunities and falls in love with Anna, who is unaware that he is already married.
Dattatraya Vakhariya is a 102-year-old man who lives with his 75-year-old son, Babulal. Dattatraya, who lives like a youngster, wants to break the world record for the oldest man living on earth.
Officers Pratap and Siddanth go to a village in Bihar to investigate the case of three missing students. They struggle with a corrupt political system and ignorant villagers.
Aarush is an unlucky man and carries his bad luck wherever he goes. His quest to find love only makes his life more miserable as he ends up in complicated situations.
In a quest to pull off a heist at a hotel in Dubai, Charlie assembles a team of non-dancers to take part in a dance competition at the hotel. They enlist the help of a bar dancer.
Mahinder, a gangster, hires Munna, a street dancer, to train him so that he can impress his lady-love, Dolly. However, when Dolly goes missing, Munna promises to bring her back.
A young man settles for the job of a taxi driver after quitting several odd jobs. However, things take a turn when he realises that the car he drives is possessed.
An undercover agent and his partner go after a thief who has stolen 2,000 crore rupees. Soon, they realise that the case is linked to the death of a crime lord and an emerging gang war.
An undercover agent and his partner go after a thief who has stolen 2,000 crore rupees. Soon, they realise that the case is linked to the death of a crime lord and an emerging gang war.
Happy, notoriously famous for his antics, is sent to fetch Lakhan so that he can meet his ailing father. But, in Australia, Happy ends up taking Lakhan's place as the king of the local underworld.
Vishal, a policeman shot by tycoon Khanna, is saved by a heart transplant. He finds himself working with the spirit of his donor, Hero, to investigate the businessman's drug racket and seek revenge.
Rajiv, a bad salesman, must find a way to save his job even though he has personal problems after encountering a devious man who breaks into his house and has other plans for him.
Six couples face problems in their lives when fate forces them to move away from each other. They must overcome these issues in order to make their love triumphant.
Gattu loves Binny but everyone in the neighbourhood forces him to treat her and all the women in the locality as his sisters. He wants to marry her and decides to fight against this prejudice.
Simmba, a corrupt police officer, works for Durva, an influential smuggler. However, his life takes an unusual turn when he decides to avenge a woman who was assaulted by Durva's brothers.
Rustom, a naval officer, shares a happy relationship with his wife Cynthia. Soon, he discovers her affair with Vikram, a close friend, and is accused of murdering him.
Abhay, a righteous thug, forcefully kidnaps grooms who demand dowry and later marries them off. Babli, his childhood sweetheart, re-enters his life and changes his priorities.
When a criminal gang slaughters an entire family, the baby survives. He is taken in by a family and the forces of nature work together to bring him face to face with the gang again when he grows up.
Rohan and Ayesha are a couple but their relationship turns sour due to rumours that they are dating different people. They decide to part ways, only to realise that they are making a mistake.
Rohan and Ayesha are a couple but their relationship turns sour due to rumours that they are dating different people. They decide to part ways, only to realise that they are making a mistake.
A rich industrialist dies just before the launch of the IPO of his company. Now, his family must keep the news of his death a secret in order to make their company's public offering a success.
Dwarka Anand serves prison time for assaulting a corrupt official while trying to obtain due compensation for his son's death. Manav, his son's friend, organises a multi-faceted campaign to free him.
Raja cheats people to make quick money. However, he seeks help from Yogi to settle scores with Varda, a billionaire based in Cape Town, when he kills his best friend, Raghav.
Akhil, an underdog and a failure, comes to know that his real father is a rich diamond merchant who has just passed away. When he goes to retrieve his wealth, he learns that a dog has inherited it.
A brave young man is unable to be with his girlfriend due to the disapproval of her parents. However, he vows to protect her after unknowingly saving her from a gang of thugs.
Narasimha, a hot-tempered mechanic with a heart of gold, protects an innocent family from the violent thugs of the city kingpin, Kariappan.
Mahinder, a gangster, hires Munna, a street dancer, to train him so that he can impress his lady-love, Dolly. However, when Dolly goes missing, Munna promises to bring her back.
A four-member team goes on a covert mission to bring back Vicky Chaddha, a money launderer, from Malaysia. However, things get complicated after one of the members gets shot.
When mobiles start flying from people's hands, Dr Vaseegaran and his robot Nila are asked to help. However, due to Pakshi Rajan having a hand in this, the two have to reinstate Chitti to defeat him.
Akash and Kiara, two heartbroken and suicidal people, find each other just as they are about to end their lives. The duo then decide to live life to the fullest until New Year's Day.
Akash and Kiara, two heartbroken and suicidal people, find each other just as they are about to end their lives. The duo then decide to live life to the fullest until New Year's Day.
Jhumroo and Ghungroo, two good-for-nothing, unemployed womanisers, realize their dream when they get jobs working at a beauty parlour run by two beautiful women.
After accidentally killing his fiancee, Anand becomes insane and is admitted to a psychiatric hospital. Tanvi, his doctor, falls in love with him, but her father does not approve, given his past.
Vipul, along with his girlfriend Shaheen and friend Saurabh, runs a hotel that is popular amongst couples. However, things take a turn when the hotel is raided by the anti-Romeo squad.
After losing the custody of his daughter Nia to his wife, Maya, Abhay dies in a car accident. However, his spirit continues to haunt their happy and peaceful life.
Jeeva and Joshna realise that they are living a life parallel to that of Srinivas and Swathi, just one year behind. When Swathi gets murdered, Jeeva must prevent Joshna from meeting the same fate.
After facing criticism from his son and employer, Shekhar, a gaming programmer, creates an invincible virtual character called Ra.One. Soon Ra.One enters the real world and kills Shekhar.
Vijay, a lookalike of criminal kingpin Don, is hired by DCP D'Silva in order to find Don's secrets. But after D'Silva dies, Vijay struggles to reveal his real identity.
Krishna unwillingly marries a village girl and moves to a new house. After seeing an abrupt and drastic change in her personality, he realises that a spirit has possessed her and tries to save her.
A young thug falls in love with a beautiful woman whose hearing is impaired. However, she seeks his help with a problem that soon puts the both of them in danger.
Kanhaiya, an adult film actor living in Thailand, falls in love with Shalu, a woman from a conservative family. In order to impress her father, he gets his colleagues to pretend to be his family.
Kanhaiya, an adult film actor living in Thailand, falls in love with Shalu, a woman from a conservative family. In order to impress her father, he gets his colleagues to pretend to be his family.
Nanhe, a tourist guide in Jaisalmer, is obsessed with his favourite actor, Bobby Deol. His dreams turn into reality when he learns that Bobby is visiting his city for a film shoot.
Punjabi man Harinder falls in love with a Kashmiri woman, Aayat. But they must overcome years of separation, due to communal riots, terrorist attacks and a major India-Pakistan war, to be together.
Viki, who belongs to the cold world of an upper-class family, finds his solace among ruthless gangsters. The absence of love and care pushes him to use his devious mind to rise up in the underworld.
Karan and Varun go to Mauritius to study but decide to stay back as they enjoy their new lifestyle. However, things take an unusual turn when their parents come to stay with them.

Lingaa, a petty thief, turns over a new leaf after realising the role his grandfather played in building a dam for the villagers. Then, he dedicates his life towards saving it from a corrupt minister.
Bored of their mundane lifestyles, three sexagenarian friends, Laali, Pinky and KD, go on a vacation to Mauritius. There, they meet Ahana and each of them try to woo her in their own style.

When Dr Sachin Mahajan is accused of killing Ayesha, his own daughter, all the evidence is against him. However, CBI Officer Paraskar starts a fresh investigation which leads him to disturbing truths.
After a suicide bomber with a bomb attached to his heart loses his memory following an accident, the Anti-Terrorism Squad sets off on a critical mission to save the country from a deadly attack.
Harsha Vardhan, a multi-millionaire, meets Charuseela, who influences him to enrol for a course on rural development. He gradually takes interest in the remote village of Devarakota.
Karan and Ahana's weekend vacation at an ancient palatial house turns into a nightmare when they are forced to fend themselves from the dark forces residing in the house.
Karan and Ahana's weekend vacation at an ancient palatial house turns into a nightmare when they are forced to fend themselves from the dark forces residing in the house.
When a wealthy alcoholic turns up dead, Detective Nilesh investigates the murder by interrogating various suspects that include her former lover, a spoilt brat and the commissioner's brother.

column4: Laali Ki Shaadi Mein Laaddoo Deewana
column5: Laddoo, a middle-class ambitious man, falls in love with beautiful Laali. However, their happiness is short-lived when they discover that Laali is pregnant.
Chandu, a henchman, and Mallik, a local hothead, join hands to form a gang. As their gang gains a reputation, tension arises between them and they eventually fall apart.
Four idlers make elaborate plans to earn money by investing in buildings but are conned by Kabir, who leaves them unemployed and penniless. Soon, they are on the prowl to avenge their humiliation.
Mahavir Phogat is forced to leave his wrestling career for conventional work. However, when he sees his daughters' potential, he trains them to become the best wrestlers and bring home a gold medal.
When a top-ranking MBBS student fails to acquire a good score in college, he tries committing suicide. As his blood spills over a tomb, he gets possessed by the mysterious spirit of a girl.
Rajjo runs a gang that strives to uplift the downtrodden and combat injustice in the village. When a corrupt politician runs for the local elections, Rajjo decides to compete against her.
Arun holds God responsible for all the problems in his life. When God appears before him and grants him divine powers, Arun thinks he can make the world a better place by granting everybody's wishes.
Friends Gopal, Lucky, Madhav and Laxman often dupe gullible people out of their money. Hilarity ensues when they target a middle-aged couple and simultaneously try wooing their pretty neighbour.
Friends Amar, Meet and Prem, who are unhappy with their married lives, decide to go for their college reunion to have fun. However, they get in trouble with the principal and a student.
Friends Amar, Meet and Prem, who are unhappy with their married lives, decide to go for their college reunion to have fun. However, they get in trouble with the principal and a student.
Sanjana's life is ruined by the evil spirit of her conjoined twin who died during surgery. In the past, her sister Anjana was jealous of her boyfriend Kabir and now seeks to steal her husband.
Mann's grandmother Bharti is scorned and ill-treated by her family. To make them realise her worth, Mann gives her a complete makeover and also convinces her to take up modelling opportunities.
After his brother is killed and father severely injured by terrorists, a young medical student quits his studies to join the Indian Police Service to wipe out the terrorists.
Aman, a Pakistani man living in London, falls in love with Asha, an Indian woman. But he must convince her parents to let them get married, despite their different nationalities.
Three friends travel to a small town where they meet Ragini, a beautiful woman. However, they soon realise that she has brought nothing but trouble in their lives.
A young man settles for the job of a taxi driver after quitting several odd jobs. However, things take a turn when he realises that the car he drives is possessed.
Param and Jasmeet's relationship undergoes stress and changes as they struggle to fulfil their dreams of relocating to England.
Two professional robbers, an illusionist, an expert make-up artist, a gadget expert and a hacker come together to steal Romanian gold ingots while it is in transit.
Upon learning of a possible threat to their country, officers Karan and Bhavana set out on a mission to London to stop a terrorist attack on India.
Nandana rejects the love-struck Karthik but unknown to them, their match was already arranged by their parents. She is not able to refuse her father and agrees while Karthik tries to win her over.
